	(text "I consider bypassing U1 and connecting \nRPM_filtered directly to the STM32.  \nRPM_filtered can then wake up the STM32 \nwhen the engine starts even if this \nsensor interface board is powerded down \nwhile sleeping. "
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 163.068 30.734 0)
		(effects
